Cincinnati Bell Inc said it has startedits previously-announced 15.75 dlr per share tender offer forall shares of Auxton Computer Enterprises Inc.    In a newspaper advertisement, the company said the tenderand withdrawal rights will expire May Five unless extended. Theoffer, which has been approved by the Auxton board and is to befollowed by a merger at the same price, is conditioned onreceipt of a majority of Auxton's voting stock on a fullydiluted basis. Reuter&#3;